00:37:59,400 --> 00:38:00,549
Pierre与 Nora结为夫妻

627
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:02,239
证婚人

628
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:04,038
Louis和 Chloe Jenssens

629
00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:07,192
Grenoble大学名誉讲师

